related_questions.question: What is CalCareers eligibility?
related_questions.snippet: An eligible list is a list of candidates who have passed all parts of the examination and can be considered for employment based on their scores. Generally the top three ranks (highest scores) of an eligible list are considered reachable and will be contacted first.
